attributes.review: This app is the worst- my phone keeps crashing every time I open it. I think it might have put some type of virus onto my phone?? Idk I am going to have to call my phone company tomorrow. Do NOT get this app!!!

attributes.title: Slow, Glitches, asks for money every two seconds
attributes.review: I hate this app so much. It’s so ugly. It uses a lot of data for no reason. It takes 2 years to load. The registrations never work. Ugh!!! Terrible app!
